{"tid":397871,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"食左16年煙用7日就戒左，你問我答","createTime":"2017-09-12T19:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-14T06:11:03.000Z","uid":81195,"like":109,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37c427d2079350915fc10e30e6979810a1ad2644","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T19:54:48.000Z","msg":"戒左先知原來食煙既人真係好撚臭"},{"pid":"9f29aa8823763c1a78d51e9a3b0cabadca740006","tid":397871,"uid":146714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T19:56:43.000Z","msg":"食開邊隻同埋點戒<br />\n我有朋友當年係打機買點買到無錢先戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7699c63f83b2c181a7ef32ba8cf2e54b9a98362","tid":397871,"uid":136252,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T19:57:33.000Z","msg":"因為你打煙炮姐"},{"pid":"1f6231d0733226c2effe9d5a2cf3b9e12eed5b13","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食開邊隻同埋點戒<br />\n我有朋友當年係打機買點買到無錢先戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭7日用戒煙貼，普通藥房有得買嗰d<br />\n<br />\n第8日開始食呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0d1xt3qy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0d1xt3qy&h=0a331406&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"336095bb16acc247bdd1a2ff3af459087d9e2bac","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:03:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為你打煙炮姐</blockquote><br />\n係食完殘留喺身陣味好撚臭，食煙嘅人唔會覺<br />\n<br />\n真係難為以前身邊唔食煙嘅人"},{"pid":"4638412ce2c5b3c23c73cd18797cc16ec98ea1fd","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:09:44.000Z","msg":"唔記得講，隻藥要醫生開，藥房冇得買"},{"pid":"b67869174ca8d2e8c9c335bac28c72853ebed1e9","tid":397871,"uid":10214,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:28:34.000Z","msg":"17年煙齡 7日戒到<br />\n唔係好信<br />\n食開咩煙"},{"pid":"c6eed0f85aa3e9a978b360d5fc3