blockquote><br />\n3 個月後冇食再揮手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3baeb89d9033f1c04e5e9f3988ab43c737c56af1","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T20:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食開邊隻同埋點戒<br />\n我有朋友當年係打機買點買到無錢先戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭7日用戒煙貼，普通藥房有得買嗰d<br />\n<br />\n第8日開始食呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0d1xt3qy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0d1xt3qy&h=0a331406&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻藥我食到斷片<br />\n唔敢再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又冇咩好明顯嘅副作用喎<br />\n<br />\n不過醫生都話之前美國有d本身有吸開毒嘅人食完隻藥會抑鬱有自殺傾向"},{"pid":"8d70f2b1e48943d722510ca4ddd1867baded8916","tid":397871,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食開邊隻同埋點戒<br />\n我有朋友當年係打機買點買到無錢先戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭7日用戒煙貼，普通藥房有得買嗰d<br />\n<br />\n第8日開始食呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0d1xt3qy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0d1xt3qy&h=0a331406&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻藥我食到斷片<br />\n唔敢再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又冇咩好明顯嘅副作用喎<br />\n<br />\n不過醫生都話之前美國有d本身有吸開毒嘅人食完隻藥會抑鬱有自殺傾向</blockquote><br />\n我有同醫生講<br />\n佢叫我停藥<br />\n因為影響工作同專注力<br />\n<br />\n之後冇再睇佢<br />\n依家自己戒到一日幾支social<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b9622d3867f815a8d68dee9ecd860fef0de0951","tid":397871,"uid":27379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:09:11.000Z","msg":"17年，點食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吸落肺嘅話，成17年，戒應該好痛苦"},{"pid":"420f1fd97bb13b93cbfc77e033fc6d44edac652b","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>17年，點食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吸落肺嘅話，成17年，戒應該好痛苦</blockquote><br />\n16咋，唔知點解變左17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇刻意忍過唔食，但真係唔想食"},{"pid":"35ba6ca9004912a03a346018ce6af01bf67b6b53","tid":397871,"uid":1977,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:16:06.000Z","msg":"你係7日戒左定戒左7日呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e8cfaa0dfe328a61a17796daaa429baaa65b833","tid":397871,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>17年，點食先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n吸落肺嘅話，成17年，戒應該好痛苦</blockquote><br />\n16咋，唔知點解變左17<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇刻意忍過唔食，但真係唔想食</blockquote><br />\nChing 仲未答人問題<br />\n<br />\n你吸落肺, 定只打煙炮先？"},{"pid":"87b01d2f0ebc3854c6cfa7d4614432f5054b7157","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係7日戒左定戒左7日呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用7日戒左，兩個月冇食"},{"pid":"4efbe6908a3eed0d683f41b9b9210248bec12d0c","tid":397871,"uid":27359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係7日戒左定戒左7日呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你試下咪知易唔易戒囉"},{"pid":"fed8d71116994b87b83c34c67d9b8d65c7700488","tid":397871,"uid":27359,"like":14,"dislike":2,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T21:22:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><