有咩好笑<br />\n你問下你屋企人想你打煙炮定吸入肺多"},{"pid":"59699bc5c1b61f031e9254feead35f913e318d45","tid":397871,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T00:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝樓主提供產品資訊"},{"pid":"f3409c76c13c7547fa98a3336ddf07bd5c4cf64b","tid":397871,"uid":17496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:13:14.000Z","msg":"有心理準備要戒一世<br />\n<br />\n利申:戒完煙破左世界紀錄,加油"},{"pid":"94251c2810f77bfa4fbbfd48a1bead923e3bc0a2","tid":397871,"uid":5899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>食開邊隻同埋點戒<br />\n我有朋友當年係打機買點買到無錢先戒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n頭7日用戒煙貼，普通藥房有得買嗰d<br />\n<br />\n第8日開始食呢隻<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0d1xt3qy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0d1xt3qy&h=0a331406&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n隻藥我食到斷片<br />\n唔敢再食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又冇咩好明顯嘅副作用喎<br />\n<br />\n不過醫生都話之前美國有d本身有吸開毒嘅人食完隻藥會抑鬱有自殺傾向</blockquote><br />\n我有同醫生講<br />\n佢叫我停藥<br />\n因為影響工作同專注力<br />\n<br />\n之後冇再睇佢<br />\n依家自己戒到一日幾支social<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢隻屬於精神科藥物 之前外國出過事停用左一排<br />\n除非煙癮嚴重到用哂戒煙貼同戒煙糖都控制唔到<br />\n否則醫生一般都唔建議一開始戒煙就用呢隻<br />\n利申：做緊藥廠"},{"pid":"33ae39a0ea5f05b8c9160ca2343a5c7505918c4f","tid":397871,"uid":120850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:32:37.000Z","msg":"直接話戒就戒邊洗咁春煩架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39830d756aba64edbba595e6b64e3a524ca04bcc","tid":397871,"uid":29070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T01:45:20.000Z","msg":"Keep住啦 戒煙係一世"},{"pid":"6421ad562786916ca50d55ae7b10f1d9963f1241","tid":397871,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T02:55:37.000Z","msg":"戒左7日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"7f4517e4ebb86316e3a76362ad50c9d8fd23ca03","tid":397871,"uid":80874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 食十幾年仲問人打煙泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef257f925250e00a46d67af1627e7c0ab071eab","tid":397871,"uid":4735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:47:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">煙鏟死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\nblock撚柒晒班死煙鏟 爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff339a2cbf2aec31f4ab13fa0c05f3c2b9748e3f","tid":397871,"uid":4329,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T03:54:45.000Z","msg":"成班人唔肯面對樓主戒到煙呢個事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己冇恆心戒煙就用自己標準黎否定人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e68a084b7481b9efba8f35b9a9e71411d232bec","tid":397871,"uid":121131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:07:07.000Z","msg":"我爸食左三十幾年都可以即刻介戒到<br />\n因為佢入院發現食煙令佢個肺功能只有一半"},{"pid":"3af4d7b799da25e664c9355a279d5ed011451eae","tid":397871,"uid":45399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:13:54.000Z","msg":"其實介煙係咪會肥？如果胃口無變的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"801d2a7fad3366a9d4d5fced5b5bd88d294e5820","tid":397871,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"其實唔難我老豆一句話貴唔食就再無食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae46175ff0ce2875a3871efd9bff6c7159286a4","tid":397871,"uid":81684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:26:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我爸食左三十幾年都可以即刻介戒到<br />\n因為佢入院發現食煙令佢個肺功能只有一半</blockquote><br />\n醫生話我繼續食落去會好快中風<br />\n但我仲係戒唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17416852ad2efdc70b60903638db67494f4f2f3","tid":397871,"uid":92166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"戒煙貼，口膠有條春用咩，咪又係尼古丁<br />\n<br />\n戒煙只有一個辦法，意志力，放假日訓夜訓，好多人戒唔成係因為佢冇得休息"},{"pid":"41f957d77d3c5e6af72b97724ede00a5244609bf","tid":397871,"uid":624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁呀 戒到煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我屋企個仆街煙齡都廿幾三十年<br />\n話咩以前去睇醫生講過想戒煙 個醫生同佢講 你食左咁多年先黎戒好易玩完<br />\n屌佢老母 搞到個仆街成撚日拎住呢點做籍口唔戒<br />\n食撚到屋企人前排又哮喘發要入院<br />\n點撚解咁多人死都唔見佢死"},{"pid":"6edd8041c88df85cf9b9e56fdcc06c7c6214deb5","tid":397871,"uid":36691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:38:49.000Z","msg":"老豆食左40幾年煙，一日一包<br />\n之前加煙稅話太貴唔食<br />\n然後食埋淨低一包就真係冇食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢咩輔助都冇用過，話唔食就唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbad2036afba70912d6827a5840483562a80a595","tid":397871,"uid":17705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:40:04.000Z","msg":"兩年唔食返至開post la"},{"pid":"1a4864627aa2dbe4657ce1dd7042ccdede106e2d","tid":397871,"uid":129048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:45:02.000Z","msg":"加油樓主"},{"pid":"049def1df39b23d7dd6abdc9b6d15e3637b6f264","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:47:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實介煙係咪會肥？如果胃口無變的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我胃口好左，但冇肥到"},{"pid":"1622afaa2d774e88e9f2023498cff3012df08a00","tid":397871,"uid":128884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:48:29.000Z","msg":"咁勁阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要食枝煙慶祝下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8551bae95dca0e888cf942a792ec984b46e73ff5","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:50:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去東華戒煙 。都戒左差不多兩年啦。完全無煙癮。第一年都會有心思思想食返既感覺。巴打們加油</blockquote><br />\n我本身都係聽完個fd去完東華講隻咁把炮先好奇去試下。<br />\n你係咩情況下想食返？<br />\n我自己黎講已經覺得食煙完全唔係一件享受嘅事"},{"pid":"98a1a4b91b9fd6ec66c3ee43877f005fc4001421","tid":397871,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"恭喜樓主唔洗死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67bf11386aab25f59c9c67f023dec65dff37cb71","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>醒左咁岩見到呢個po<br />\n好想去戒煙</blockquote><br />\n戒啦。唔食煙果種感覺係好清新</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋好自由"},{"pid":"75b88e6f1cc564883ca24d7f5942241409444376","tid":397871,"uid":15945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:53:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戒煙貼，口膠有條春用咩，咪又係尼古丁<br />\n<br />\n戒煙只有一個辦法，意志力，放假日訓夜訓，好多人戒唔成係因為佢冇得休息</blockquote><br />\n食煙最傷身係焦油同一氧化碳<br />\n轉食尼古丁代替品頂住鋪癮都好好多啦<br />\n至少身邊d人唔洗挨二手煙先"},{"pid":"758ac34188ac1cf0a22cf271cf1bc8492bb8e9e6","tid":397871,"uid":66828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"食左4年 戒左一個月<br />\n早幾日試下食返枝 臭到頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著就連僅餘既癮都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由上次個一枝計 已戒1星期<br />\n互勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"501cefb28d0d2be6fc19acbad5005614ea6b91ec","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:00:45.000Z","msg":"我老豆都係食左幾十年<br />\n話唔食就唔食嗰d<br />\n男人去到五六十歲嗰種意志真係好撚有型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就自問唔得喇<br />\n所以有藥食仲要唔駛錢我覺得好岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb434f7a58774da8640d0a15ca8be4c2d7d479d","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:03:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左4年 戒左一個月<br />\n早幾日試下食返枝 臭到頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟著就連僅餘既癮都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由上次個一枝計 已戒1星期<br />\n互勉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我而家有食完煙冇耐嘅fd上車<br />\n即刻頂唔順要開窗<br />\n一諗起以前自由係咁撚臭就覺得好對唔住d唔食煙嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28dd9fdbfddb65b0252bee0584e0274dc857fbd6","tid":397871,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:05:30.000Z","msg":"其實唔洗用自己錢買藥<br />\n政府戒煙熱線又有藥又有針灸又有人跟進你戒成點<br />\n全部免費"},{"pid":"da43c2343abd763d508e308df2ae24f35e262b10","tid":397871,"uid":81256,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:09:21.000Z","msg":"食左8年<br />\n近期轉食iqos<br />\n發現食返真煙好臭<br />\n但iqos又好似食糖咁，唔太成癮<br />\n於是兩樣都無食<br />\niqos真係戒煙神物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9cc0f5a45b09b28304386f1fa30c30438532fd0","tid":397871,"uid":61325,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:11:32.000Z","msg":"老豆食左三十幾年煙<br />\n有心臟病入廠之後<br />\n諗一諗我兩兄弟<br />\n就從此無食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fec76ec6f745a3ca81ea5d0f9c1b467f6f557c1","tid":397871,"uid":25152,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:15:04.000Z","msg":"食左8年 戒足8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由第一日開始食煙就一日一包 係外國生活好枯燥 身邊9成人都食煙 有無咩tips"},{"pid":"b436bbed3c6a278189f92d2f762ba4492212c777","tid":397871,"uid":72276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:19:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老豆食左三十幾年煙<br />\n有心臟病入廠之後<br />\n諗一諗我兩兄弟<br />\n就從此無食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好感動，我老豆食咗四十年成日覺得無事<br />\n唔肯戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7d600538e67dcb31ff2fa1c721f7011fd3a93a","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老豆食左三十幾年煙<br />\n有心臟病入廠之後<br />\n諗一諗我兩兄弟<br />\n就從此無食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好感動，我老豆食咗四十年成日覺得無事<br />\n唔肯戒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢未搵到個理由戒煙姐<br />\n我自己之前都有諗過戒<br />\n但又真係實在搵唔到咩理由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真又唔係特別想咁長命<br />\n健康問題又暫時未出現<br />\n今次戒煙可以話係個意外收鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4bd6bc0bef18ae4657ad47e67a0ae957e7022fc","tid":397871,"uid":128884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:33:04.000Z","msg":"食左16年 巴打今年幾歲？<br />\n你會唔會係我阿爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2adc25163ac966b9ce88d8a601cd40b6e2f397","tid":397871,"uid":84277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"其實食煙係心癮，係習慣<br />\n未食過啲細蚊仔話尼古丁上癮真係得啖笑<br />\n利申：戒左兩年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"040487a1532e9ced139410d08f19a3f5614b0533","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食左16年 巴打今年幾歲？<br />\n你會唔會係我阿爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要你阿媽會清楚d<br />\n<br />\n15歲睇完花樣年華就自學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eug2x4ow\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feug2x4ow&h=97096d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時覺得點解可以食煙食得咁撚有型"},{"pid":"2e33481d7f7cd76f31bb31c66e40e0fe05179e99","tid":397871,"uid":141582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"睇你生活圈子同健康 仲要好有決心<br />\n識1個有重病 識1個要結婚生仔<br />\n都係廿年煙癮 1-2個月戒左<br />\n之後都無食返 仲對煙幾反感"},{"pid":"fffeec59aa829c0c6eea723ba2b9698dc1b93b54","tid":397871,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去東華戒煙 。都戒左差不多兩年啦。完全無煙癮。第一年都會有心思思想食返既感覺。巴打們加油</blockquote><br />\n我本身都係聽完個fd去完東華講隻咁把炮先好奇去試下。<br />\n你係咩情況下想食返？<br />\n我自己黎講已經覺得食煙完全唔係一件享受嘅事</blockquote><br />\n東華果個唔係中醫針灸咩？<br />\n試過去過淨係派口交<br />\n<br />\n政府果個做完問卷<br />\n就答十零支都唔嚴重<br />\n口膠都廢事派<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d02322eef88835c1d5fb905585f34266a95ba4a","tid":397871,"uid":128884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:53:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>食左16年 巴打今年幾歲？<br />\n你會唔會係我阿爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要你阿媽會清楚d<br />\n<br />\n15歲睇完花樣年華就自學<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/eug2x4ow\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Feug2x4ow&h=97096d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當時覺得點解可以食煙食得咁撚有型</blockquote><br />\n我阿爸真係幾似梁朝偉"},{"pid":"8a4d32fd55c53e7b9317d4dcb9bd79b9b98025d0","tid":397871,"uid":15880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>因為你打煙炮姐</blockquote><br />\n係食完殘留喺身陣味好撚臭，食煙嘅人唔會覺<br />\n<br />\n真係難為以前身邊唔食煙嘅人</blockquote><br />\n成陣屍臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5d4c6dfb71dc856ca06c079b4820f9808f1b774","tid":397871,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"唔驚生野?"},{"pid":"1643e3ccd70899cd0d93877b7094ef7d97df7567","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔驚生野?</blockquote><br />\n要生d咩？"},{"pid":"44ba667a685f0bc66d1dd77effc4db14902724e3","tid":397871,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:22:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔驚生野?</blockquote><br />\n要生d咩？</blockquote><br />\ncancer"},{"pid":"8415c6002744acea3d34ee72844eba2136891f9a","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:23:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔驚生野?</blockquote><br />\n要生d咩？</blockquote><br />\ncancer</blockquote><br />\n呼吸與心跳都會有機會生cancer個喎"},{"pid":"445f6331b851847dbbe75ee2876fbbca45c59f4a","tid":397871,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:24:06.000Z","msg":"繼續食啦"},{"pid":"4f6f71bb8a78ff229a5b04f8af2a54dd61ba3c70","tid":397871,"uid":50839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"樓主未戒煙之前一日食幾多？開始左用煙貼之後即刻一支都冇食過？<br />\n利申：想戒"},{"pid":"aba8771604814f14dc9aff617b93538903d9d3b1","tid":397871,"uid":105446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔驚生野?</blockquote><br />\n要生d咩？</blockquote><br />\ncancer</blockquote><br />\n呼吸與心跳都會有機會生cancer個喎</blockquote><br />\n但你唔驚?"},{"pid":"abe4113ab5e9b28024f8807ac3b3e734590932a6","tid":397871,"uid":120250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:51:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 忍住啊"},{"pid":"10f086d6b9ea39d002401a1f2d1b11c0fea546a7","tid":397871,"uid":81195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:56:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主未戒煙之前一日食幾多？開始左用煙貼之後即刻一支都冇食過？<br />\n利申：想戒</blockquote><br />\n未戒之前大概三日食兩包<br />\n開始用戒煙貼嗰陣想食嘅次數少左好多，第一日已經少左一半，然後每日越黎越少。<br />\n到開始食藥冇耐，點著支煙食一啖已經食唔落去想掉，食完個人想嘔又頭暈，總之好唔舒服，一d都唔享受"}]}